TopicTitle: Waiter, theres a _____________ in my soup!

Articles.Content:
It's pushing you towards a interstellar orbit.

Waiter! There's Yoda in my soup!

Don't worry, it's just teaching you to use the Force.

WAITER!!! There's a freakin' gun in my soup!

Hand over the documents before my friend under the table, who is holding the gun, punishes you for delaying.

Waiter, I'm pretty certain that's arsenic in my soup.

Good, one less of you to deal with.

Waiter, there's a man in my soup saying "are you paying too much for your car insurance?"

Oh, him. Ignore him, maybe throw him away?

Waiter, there's a damn NERVA in my soup.

well its disarmed so enjoy

waiter why is there a Bender in my soup! And it just set my soup on fire

Well, then just ask him to leave, he'll just start his own soup with blackjacks and hookers.

Waiter why is there a baby space kraken in my space soup?

Terribly sorry sir, you seem to have ordered the dinner and a show. The Baby Kraken seems to be performing an interpretive dance.

WAITER!!! There's a deck of cards in my soup!

That's because the soup is PAPER THIN! (because cards are made of paper)

Waiter, there's an SRB in my soup/breadsticks/fettucine alfredo.... yeah I usually eat at Olive Garden.

Oh dear. This is embarrassing. You ordered mashed potatoes as a side, not the soup.

Waiter, there seems to be glowing shrine to Gozer in my soup.

No idea what that is. I imagine it's safe to eat.

Waiter, there's a nuke in my soup!!!

Just eat it, I'm sure that you, the restaurant and 3/4 of the city will be fine.

Waiter, there's a cannon ball in my soup.

Have fun eating it, 'cause it's gonna explode.

WAITER! There is nothing on this table!

You haven't ordered yet. Would you like our special of the day: arsenic soup?

Waiter! There's a bird splashing around in my chicken noodle soup!

Well, it is a chicken in your chicken noodle soup.

Waiter, Discovery is in my soup...

Well, you could say this shocking, discovery, huh?

Waiter... There's no soup in my soup!

that's 'cause it's chicken linguine, not chicken noodle soup, smart one

Waiter, there's no waiter! (So obviously I never ordered)

May I take your order?

WAITER, there's no one in here!

I'm just a voice in your head, go get your own soup!

Waiter! The grim reaper is standing on my soup, along with many of my dead relatives!

That's because it's your grampa's order, kid!

Waitress!!! There's RCS thrusters around my soup bowl, and they are malfunctioning!!! >:^[

You ordered hydrazine soup. Enjoy the burning esophagus!

WAITER. There is a waiter in my soup!

well hurry up and eat it so i can get on with my job

WAITER theres a Danny2462 in my soup!

We put him in there to find all the bugs in it. Of course, that bowl won't last long

Waiter, I have the letter P in my soup!

Terribly sorry sir, we did not realise you wanted pea soup.

Waiter, waiter, There seems to be a recursive function in my soup.

I have no idea what that is. I'm sure you'll be fine.

Waiter, there's a WWII in my soup!
